The evidence with the title 'Republican John Boehner replaces Nancy Pelosi as House speaker ' says Jan 5, 2011  ... In his speech Boehner said : "we gather here today at a time of great challenges: nearly one in 10 of our neighbours are looking for work , healthcare costs are still rising for families and small businesses , our spending has caught up with us and our debt will soon eclipse the size of our entire economy . ".
